      "review_summary": "The PR adds async credential/config-resolution helpers and switches selected auth epoch, auth storage, and config-value reads toward async APIs.\n\nPR surface: Source +400. Total +400 across 4 files.\n\nReproducibility: yes. for source-level reproduction: current main still contains synchronous keychain, auth-file, and config-command reads in reachable auth-provider code. I did not run a live current-main Gateway/Telegram stall reproduction in this read-only review.",
